snippet.title: TIEBREAK: Official game of the ATP and WTA | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
TIEBREAK: Official game of the ATP and WTA will be released on 22 August 2024 for PlayStation®5, PlayStation®4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One and PC (Steam). 
The Nintendo Switch™ version will be launched at a later date.

Join us:
X(Twitter): https://x.com/Tiebreakthegame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Tiebreakthegame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tiebreakthegame/
